'''Lauik Kaspia''' atau '''Danau Kaspia''' marupoan kumpulan aia nan paliang gadang lawehnyo nan talatak di ateh tanah daratan [[bumi]], sainggo dapek digologan sabagai [[danau]] nan palaing gadang di dunia atau buliah pulo disabuik sabagai [[lauik]].<ref name=web1>"[http://www.caspianenvironment.org/newsite/Caspian-Background.htm Caspian Sea - Background]". Caspian Environment Programme. 2009. Diakses 11 September 2012.</ref><ref>"[http://www.esa.int/esaEO/SEM5GYTLWFE_index_0.html ESA: Observing the Earth – Earth from Space: The southern Caspian Sea]". ESA.int. Diakses 2007-05-25.</ref> Danau iko mamiliaki pamukoan salaweh 371.000 km2 (143.200 kaki pasagi) (indak tamasuak [[laguna]] [[Garabogazköl Aylagy]] di [[Turkmenistan]]) jo volume aia 78.200 km3 (18.800 kubik mil).<ref name="LakeNet">[http://www.worldlakes.org/lakedetails.asp?lakeid=8762 Lake Profile: Caspian Sea]. ''LakeNet.''</ref> Danau iko tasumbek, indak ado saluaan aia kaluanyo (''endorheic basin''), sarato babateh ka barat lauik jo [[Rusia]], ka barat jo [[Azerbaijan]], ka salatan jo [[Iran]], ka tenggara jo Turkmenistan, dan ka timur lauik jo [[Kazakhstan]].

Banso-banso kuno nan tingga dakek pasisianyo maanggap danau ko sabagai lauik, kamungkian karano aianyo nan taraso asin atau bisa juo karano lawehnyo. Kadar garam danau ko kiro-kiro 1,2%, yaitu sapetigo kadar garam lauik pado umumnyo.

